name: hibiscus afghan square
notes:
this is a fun afghan square, will look great as part of a sampler afghan or on its own.  intermediate level with a few post stitches and overlay crochet techniques.  have fun with colors!

this is a featured design in the 2025 moogly block cal - see moogly.com for all the free patterns and check out the facebook moogly cal group for inspiration.

pattern free on my blog http://julieyeagerdesigns.com

pattern support at the julie yeager designs board on ravelry!
